    <section name="Functions: FnCalendar">

      

      <subsection name="1. Overview">

        <p>
        	<b><a href="http://www.op4j.org/apidocs/org/op4j/functions/FnCalendar.html">FnCalendar</a></b> is a <em>function class</em>
        	containing a lot of static methods to work with Calendar objects. Those static methods return functions that take 
        	a <b>Calendar</b> object as its input or output (depending on the function). It includes 
        	conversions to String, to Calendar and adding days to a Calendar among others.        	  
        </p>
        
      </subsection>

